{"tid":2162731,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"武肺似是沒了期","createTime":"2020-08-18T09:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T18:09:04.000Z","uid":111088,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2eac2f37cc8ea6bff285c7409940ab450b2730fb","tid":2162731,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">武肺 妨礙我呼吸空氣<br />\n不過林鄭 仲信奉 維尼<br />\n唔封關嗎　喂柒婆　其實柒夠未<br />\n<br />\n武肺　逢六點先會搞你你</span><br />\n只要尋覓　此刻的奧秘<br />\n你的體態　你面容　你心中歡喜<br />\n<br />\n實在沒法把愛留起<br />\n惟求能在這夜　翻天覆地<br />\n最美　一消失<br />\n不會等你<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">武肺似是沒了期</span><br />\n要說永遠　偏偏不合理<br />\n愛上了你卻在我心中已預期<br />\n離別你　懷念你　尋覓你<br />\n卻未忘記你"},{"pid":"0c9154ecf5f1f37d13def200ac39b96d19650f30","tid":2162731,"uid":185669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3a2894ff6b2a203820108d0cd8c802986e201b","tid":2162731,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a7a8fdeaa772c4bc6e4fd00c8a85d44ebb23117c","tid":2162731,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c9154ecf5f1f37d13def200ac39b96d19650f30","tid":2162731,"uid":185669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:23:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又冇唔啱音"},{"pid":"3362fc6e4033effbcb135b5bfe41ddecd6ea0432","tid":2162731,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf3a2894ff6b2a203820108d0cd8c802986e201b","tid":2162731,"uid":281492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:23:18.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4041750378